 tongue, Allah will cover his faults. Whoever restrains his anger, Allah will restrain his punishment on the Day of Resurrection. Whoever apologizes to Allah, Allah Almighty will accept his apology.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/hardship-debt-shade-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1841,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Helping others in the shade of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would love to be shaded in the shade of Allah, let him help someone in hardship or waive a loan.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad\u00a015520 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/21\/cancel-regretful-sales\/","url_meta":{"origin":1841,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sales: Allah forgives those who cancel regretful sales","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever cancels the sale of a regretful Muslim, Allah will cancel his mistakes on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2199 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/allah-shade-relief\/","url_meta":{"origin":1841,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Allah shades those who give relief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever grants respite to someone in difficulty or relieves him, Allah will shade him on the Day of Resurrection when there is no shade but His.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1306 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19188,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/19\/allah-covers-faults-brother\/","url_meta":{"origin":1841,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Faults: Allah covers faults of those who covered faults","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2014","fo